-------------------------------
-First Time Installation Steps-
-------------------------------

1.a Download the iptables-master.zip
	OR
1.b git clone git://git.sygil.org/iptables.git /your/directory/

2. copy sample to your file starting name
	cp sample iptables.sh
	
3. Modify iptables.sh for your server or computer 

4. Enjoy

-------------------------------
---Update Installation Steps---
-------------------------------
	
If your site need an update :
	
with git place you on your site folder
 /your/directory/
and execute git pull
	
OR
	
download the new portal-master.zip on http://sygil.org
	
	
